hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'd like to send this letter by europharmashop.com Transportation Department spokeman Veronica Beyer said both the Prada Marfa and the Playboy bunny are considered signs under Texas law, meaning it's something intended to advertise, including logos. The bunny sculpture is the magazine's iconic logo, while the fake store has the Prada logo on its awnings. Under US law, a permit is needed to display signs along a US highway.
